## Project Structure

```text
app/                 # App Router: routes, layouts, route handlers (app/api/**/route.ts)
components/          # Shared UI (Navigation, StoreCard, theme) not tied to one route
lib/                 # Utilities, auth, Prisma helpers, domain logic
prisma/              # PostgreSQL schema + migrations
prisma-mongo/        # MongoDB (mock pack payloads)
tests/               # Jest tests
public/              # Static assets
```

